#Circular consumption and production of electronic devices
An approach to measuring durability, upgradeability, reusability, obsolescence and premature recycling

[comment]: <> (Consumers use the same electronic devices for the longest time, either internally, or by collaborating with external agents so that these devices are reused and recycled properly, but recycled no prematurely, only when they can no longer be used or reused by anyone else. )

.footnote[Go to [project site](https://www.ereuse.org)]
