##Usage rate per model
***
###Indicates the rate of devices per model still in usage. 
> **UM: The Usage rate per a given model M**   
> UM(M) = (Devices in use per model <sub>M</sub>)  `&#47` (Total of devices per model <sub>M</sub>)   
   
