##Reusability
***
###Indicates how reusable a device is
>**R: Reusability per device**   
>R(D) = % devices of the model in use with similar performance


```remark
Before getting rid of my laptop Dell Latitude model E6440 
with value of use 3. I check that there are 70% of these
still in operation.  I can safely say that it is 70% 
reusable.
```

[comment]: <> (ccc)

]

