.left-column[
  ## Metrics
  ###Upgradeability
  ###Reusability
  ###Reusability Potential
  ###Premature Recycling 
]
.right-column[
<img src="./imgs/dell-latitude-e6440.jpg" alt="drawing" width="80" align="right" style="padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 0px"/>
##Premature Recycling 
***
###Indicates the reusability potential we are discarding if we recycle (destroy) the device.
   
>**PR: Premature Recycling per device**   
>PR(D) = Reusability Potential

   

```remark
I discard for recycling my laptop Dell Latitude 
model E6440, with a 90% Reusability Potential.
I am prematurely recycling 90% of my laptop.
```

[comment]: <> (ccc)

]

